\id 2PE Kharam: Bible Translation 1st Edition 
\h 2 Peter 
\toc1 PETER Inni Huuina Chemajia 
\toc2 2 Peter 
\toc3 2 Pet 
\mt1 PETER 
\mt2 Inni Huuina Chemajia 
\imt1 Chonglamsaat 
\ip \bk Hiwa 2 Peter Chemajia hi\bk* Tirton Peter in imajia eii tia aril, takkha awini kasing-kathei angjet inchu akatuun eii tia ngaidonmu. Hiwahi Peter rathuulla tu ka-ang inkhat in imajia lei-echa inti. Akamajiapa khan hinthoa aril khachu, Jisu ringkhuo khat-um aru ka-ekhet ah meelsuo-inthuulna sakhi kha ama eii ati (2 Peter 1:17-18). Hiwa chemajia hi Peter imajia e-inchu Christa innei suonuk kum 65-69 suungnga ama athi makma Rome makheiya imajia lei-ete. 1 Peter chemajia amajia suona apha thunna Peter innum hiwahi ama inni huuina chemajia eii ati (2 Peter 3:1). Ama'n Christian rakip diang hiwa chemajia hi imajia eii. Peter in hiwa chemajia hi kangamna ngai ringkhuo katha ah omnasik malung masokpi nasik ah khat-um inmani kha chong peya akatuunmak ocha ngai juimak nasik imajia eii (2 Peter 2). Tu ka-ang mi ngai'n Jisu ajuokir nasik apha kasoottak alei kati ngai inloppui maknasik ama'n inmani kha aleimasok. Khawa rathuulla ama'n Pathian chu insuum emak takkha mirakip kha sanringsik manuom tia arilsuok (2 Peter 3:8-9). Hiwajarra eii akatha ringkhuo inkhat-ah niringsik hi (2 Peter 3:14). 
\iot Asuungnga kaom Chong 
\io1 1. Peter in ama chemajia kateel ngaidiang iril khat-um apumtak meel imalar. \ior (1:1-2)\ior* 
\io1 2. Ama'n inmani kha akatha ringkhuo-ah ringnasik amin-ngaidon ajarchu Pathian in eini um namintor. \ior (1:3-21)\ior* 
\io1 3. Ama'n akatuunmak ocha ngai chungnga chong apeii halli ajuohekna ah angme akatuunmak ocha ngaidiang kasuoksik jarra aril. \ior (2:1-22)\ior* 
\io1 4. Khawasuo Peter in kangamna ngaikha akatha ringkhuo ah ringnasik khat-um Jisu woini huuina ajuo nasik-ah insuuknasik malung masok ah aleiminhek. \ior (3:1-17)\ior* 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Jisu Christa suok le tirton inkhat kachang Simon Peter in, 
\p eini Pathian khat-um kanasanpa Jisu Christa dikna khan eini ngamna angnga amankatam ngamna ipe ngaidiang: 
\p  
\v 2 Pathian le Nipumi Jisu ningjetna khanna inphut, minriang khat-um akadai kha ningchungnga kasip-ah omrase. 
\s1 Pathian Koina khat-um Kadangna 
\p  
\v 3 Ama apumtak athana li apoina tum kachang sik-ah anakakoipa kha eini'n nijetna ah inphut, akatuun biaklam ringkhuo ah ringnasik arei kaom Pathian ranak rakip kha einidiang anapejei.  
\v 4 Khawa jarra hiwa kutchoi ngaihin ajar eya hiwa nuoipilchung manuomna hin mangna sik-ah inphut nangni'n ningsuokthei nasik khat-um Pathian omchan kha tum ningchang theinasik, hinthoa ama'n einidiang chong inkhitna kalokkhet khat-um amankatam kutchoi ngaikha anapejei.  
\v 5 Hiwa jarra ningmatorseng tho-inlang nangni ngamna khan akatha kha thundelru halli nangni thana khan singna-theina kha thundelru;  
\v 6 nangni singna-theina chungnga pum-insur matorna thundelru; ningpum-insur matorna chungnga deiraatna thundelru; ningdeiraatna chungnga Pathian jetna kha thundelru;  
\v 7 Nangni Pathian jetna chungnga Christian inriangna kha thundelru; nangni Christian inriangna chungnga minriang kha thundelru.  
\v 8 Hiwa ngaihi nangni sik-ah arei kaom kul ngaikha eii, nangni'n hiwa ngaihi kheella ningnei inchu, khawa ngaikha in Nipumi Jisu Christa jetna-theina khan nangni ngaikha inringchak khat-um kathozoot namin ete.  
\v 9 Takkha tu e-innum hiwa kul ngaihi innei mak inchu, kalaak-ah kamu matormak mitkacho halli akatheng inmanuwa inphut naminthiangjei tikha inmaniljei. 
\p  
\v 10 Khawajarra, ulenai ngai, Pathian nakoina le anakadangna kha kheella mincheen nasik thoru; nangni'n kha ningtho inchu, angtikniteii ning-inngamna kha mathaan nutun.  
\v 11 Hinthoa Nipumi le Nakasanpa Jisu Christa hektik kaommak Rengramma luutnasik nangnidiang ranak rakip kha innapesik eii. 
\p  
\v 12 Halli nangni'n ningkeiluut jei akatuun khan kacheet-ah ning-om hi ningjetsa ejei-innum, hiwa jarra pha rakip ah kei'n kanaminngaidon sik eii.  
\v 13 Hiwa jarra kei'n karing laiseng nangni ngaidonna malung masokchaksik hi kei sik-ah akatuun eii tia kangaidon.  
\v 14 Ajarchu Nipumi Jisu Christa in keidiang inthiangnga narilpi angnga, hiwa akamangsik kapum hi innot-ah kamathaansik ejei ti kei'n kajet.  
\v 15 Khawajarra kei'n kathi suonuk hiwa jar hi apha rakip ah nangni sik-ah ningngaidon nasik lam inkhat kei imator sengnga penasik kei'n kathosik eii. 
\s1 Christa Lurna Kamu ngai 
\p  
\v 16 Nipumi Jisu Christa in ranak kaneitak ah ajuosik chonghi nangnidiang kinnaminjet pha inbool thurchi ngaikha kinjuiya kinril emak, kinmittak in alok-alianna kha kinleimujei. 
\p  
\v 17 Pa Pathian in amadiang kayana khat-um lurna apelai, Chungnung khet lurna-ah inphut rasa kha amadiang ajuopha, “Hiwahi kiminriangtak Kasapa kha eii, ama chungnga kamalung atai,” atilai takkhan keini um khawakhan kinleiom!  
\v 18 Keini'n amale inruoiya ching inthiang chungnga kin omsuom lai, marwaanna inphut hiwa rasa kajuohi kinpumtak in kinjet. \rq Matt 17:1-5; Mk 9:2-7; Luk 9:28-35\rq* 
\p  
\v 19 Khawajarra Pathian chongkachoi ngai'n inleiril chongkhan kheella eini namin-ngamna eii. Hiwahi Khuowar maklaiseng aziingna munna kawar sariakmei khat-um nangni malung suungnga akawar ziingtiang sorpa ka-ang kha eii, khawajarra nangni'n khawa khan katha-ah malung-minluutsik eii.  
\v 20 Mansakhet-ah, nangni'n hiwahi ngaidonru, Chong-inthiang suungnga Pathian chongkachoi ngai ileiril chong ngaihi tu inkhat innum apumtak in malet matornuni.  
\v 21 Ajarchu Pathian-chongkachoi ngai'n inrilsuok chongpui hi miring lungdouwa inphut hongkasuok sup-eii emak, takkha mi ngai'n Pathian diangnga inphut akajuo chongpui inleiril phakhan Ratha Inthiang inruoipuina nuoiya inmani'n inleiril eii. 
\c 2  
\s1 Akatuunmak ocha ngai 
\p  
\v 1 Khawalaiya mi ngai karra akadikmak pathian chongkachoi ngaikha inlei-inlar, halli hiwa hile in-ang rip-ah akatuunmak ocha ngai'n nangni karra inlahong inlarsik eii. Inmani'n kakatanpa Karu kha hongzootnunu, halli inmani'n mangnasik ka-eii katuunmak minchuna kha laheichoi inta, inmanitak chungnga jetlei theileiya mangna kha inlaheichoi sik eii.  
\v 2 Kha-ennum, mi katamtak in inmani kathamak taksa manuomna lamtiang inlajuisik eii, halli inmani chuontho jarra akatuun Lam kha mileiilak ngai'n kase-ah inlarilsik eii.  
\v 3 Hiwa akatuunmak ocha ngai mahamlian jarra inbool thurchi nangnidiang inril ngaikhan nemnasik inlathosik eii. Ajarchu tiallaiya inphut inmani chongkatanpa insuuk suojei, halli inmani Kaminmang sikpa kha intheiya omjei. 
\p  
\v 4 Ajarchu marwaan tirton manu katho ngaikha Pathian in hooimak, takkha Chongtan nasik Nikhuo min-ngaak ah inmani ngaikha thirruiya inkhit ah aziingna meikhur khan deengluut-ah inmani kha adajei. 
\p  
\v 5 Nuoipilchung maruo kha Pathian in hooimak, takkha nuoipilchungnga pathian kajetmak mi ngai chungnga tui minlian; akatuun chongkaril Noah bitkha miring sarile aleisanring. \rq Inphut 6:1–7:24\rq* 
\p  
\v 6 Pathian in Sodom li Gomorrah khuopui ngaikha zootmak ah, meiya aleiminmang, halli pathian kajetmak ngai chungnga kasuoksik minkhina hi aleimin eii. \rq Inphut 19:24\rq* 
\p  
\v 7 Ama'n dan kaneimak omchan kathamak katho mi ngai'n inleiminpoong mi katha, Lot kha aleisan. \rq Inphut 19:1-16\rq* 
\p  
\v 8 Mi kathapa kha inmani karra aleiom, halli ziing-nisuo ah ama'n inmani chuon kathamak ngaikha amu khat-um ajet-ah ama malung kapoongnga aleidei.  
\v 9 Halli khawajarra Pathian kajet mi ngaikha inmani poongna ah inphut Pumi'n angtho thoa sansikme, halli akathamak ngaikha rachaakna nuoiya Chongtan Nikhuo sik-ah angtho thoa dasikme ti ajet,  
\v 10 aru ka-ekhet ah inmani taksa manuom kachok khat-um Pathian thomatorna kha kazootmak ngai, 
\p Hiwa akatuunmak ocha ngai'n chimu khat-um inkuor angar, halli chungtiangnga lurna kanei ngaikha kayana neimu; khawa rathuulla, inmani'n inmani kha kase-ah inleiril.  
\v 11 Marwaan tirton ngai'n akatuunmak ocha ngai neek-ah kangar khat-um karaat inkheel innum, Pumi maikuungnga inmani chungnga kase-ah rilla noonkuung leipemu.  
\v 12 Surliya thatsik ah injuonei pangringnga karing i-kajetmak ramsa neek-ah inmani ngaihi akatha emu; inmani'n injet lekmak kha kase-ah inril. Inmani kha ramsa ngai angnga inlaminmangsik eii,  
\v 13 halli inmani'n poongna inpe angnga inmani um inlaminpoongsik eii. Inmani taksa manuom khachu suunwarra kahur-kakhiang intho kha inmani khopna eii; inmani'n minmangnasik lam ngaikhan inhoi laiseng inrokpui, halli nangni bubakna khan inhong-inchelpha injakna halli maimookna inneisik eii!  
\v 14 Inmani'n iteii entok manuommu takkha zool-inthai puisik numeisa ngaikha in-entok; inmani manu inthozoot kha angtikniteii kakhop ommak. Inmani'n ratha ah kasuol mi ngaikha surnasik ah inkeiruoi. Inmani malung ngaikha mahamlian nasik ininsuuk jei. Halli Pathian khomaak saamna nuoiya inmani in-omjei! 
\p  
\v 15 Inmani'n lam katuun kha inmathaanna halli akathamak lamtiang sial kamanuom Beor sapa Balaam injuiya, inmani'n inlam inminchaijei \rq Teelna 22:4-35\rq* 
\p  
\v 16 halli salungdai in ama manu jarra ranjei. Ama salungdai khan miring rasa ah chong ahongrilla Pathian chongkachoi inweet chuontho kha mindajei. 
\p  
\v 17 Hiwa mi ngaihi kahuul tuiring ngai khat-um thipui seemjuon suumphai ngai ka-ang in-eii; inmani sik-ah Pathian in inthuukkhet kaziingmun kha adapijei.  
\v 18 Inmani'n in-orna khat-um kamo chong inril, halli ringkhuo katuunmak ah kaom mi ngai karra heikasuoklim ngaikha surnasik ah omchan kathamak taksa manuomna ngaikha inleineiman.  
\v 19 Inmani inpumtak kathamak suok inchanglai khan, inmani diang ninglenuomma omnasik chong ininkhit, ajarchu eini kanamator inkhattak suok kha ni-ejei.  
\v 20 Inmani Nipumi khat-um Nakasanpa Jisu Christa jetna-theina jarra, nuoipilchung kathamak ranak ah inphut aheikasuokjei mi ngaikha woikhat inlet-ah asurli inmani amator inchu, inphutna omchan kathamak kha neek-ah ajuohekna ah hiwa mi ngai omchan hi kase detkha esik eii.  
\v 21 Inmani diangnga inpe akatuun lam kha injetsuoli chongpeii inthiangnga inphut inkirnooksik neek achu inleijet lekmak khan inmanisik thadoomsik eii. 
\p  
\v 22 Inmani diang kasuok khan chongngil ngaikha atuun ti kha amalar: “Ui khan ama maluok kha abak kirnook” halli “Wok tuikabuol suokhan dialbuk ah buol abuolkir.” \rq Chongil 26:11\rq* 
\c 3  
\s1 Pumi Juonasik Chong-inkhitna 
\p  
\v 1 Minriang kaom kasap ngai, tuunna kei'n nangni diangnga kimajia hi inni huuina chemajia kha eii. Chemajia inni ngai suungnga ningngaidonna khan kase katha inthiang tak-ah asuokthei nasik kei'n hiwa ngaihi kinamasok eii.  
\v 2 Tiallaiya Pathian chongkachoi inthiang ngai chongril, halli Kanasanpa Pumi makheiya inphut chongpeii nangni tirton ngai'n innapekha ningngaidonsik hi kei'n kamanuom. 
\p  
\v 3 Mansakhet-ah, nangni'n hiwa hi jetru, khawa khachu nuk-intong nikhuoni ngaikhan inmani inpumtak taksa-manuom khan inringkhuo kamintor mi lekkhat ngaikha hong-inlar inta, inmani'n nangnikha inna-innuipuisik eii \rq Jud 18\rq* 
\p  
\v 4 halli “Kajuosik eii tia chong-inkhit ama kha, chong-inkhit mak abe? Ama hun omme? Eini nipi-nipu ngaikha inleithijei, takkha angrakip nuoipil inbool makheiya inphut tuunkatung in-ang rip-ah aom!” intisik eii. 
\p  
\v 5 Tiallai khan Pathian in chong apeya marwaan li nuoipil hi lei-inbool. Nuoipilchung hi tui in inbool eii halli tui makheiya eii. Khawa akatuun kha inmani'n manil kinte tia inmanil eii, \rq Inphut 1:6-9\rq* 
\p  
\v 6 halli khawa tuiya inphut tui-minlianna manmasituol maruo kha aleiminmangjei. \rq Inphut 7:11\rq* 
\p  
\v 7 Takkha tuunna kaom marwaan le nuoipilchung hichu meiya minmang sik-ah in-angrip Pathian chongpe khan ahooiya ida eii. Inmani ngaikha pathian kajetmak mi ngai chongtan nikhuosik khat-um minmang sik-ah ida ngaikha in-eii. 
\p  
\v 8 Takkha minriang kaom kasap ngai, manil maksik inkhat om! Pumi mitmu achu nisuokhat li kum lisingkhat hi inthen ommak; ama diangchu hiwa inni hi in-angrip eii. \rq Minpkla 90:4\rq* 
\p  
\v 9 Mi lekkhat in inngaidon angnga, Pumi chong-inkhitna khan ama'n thosik ah insuummak, khawa rathuulla, ama'n einisik kasoot-ah nadeipi, ajarchu tu-inkhat um kamangsik ama'n manuommak, takkha mirakip in inmanuwa inphut inmalung inhei-inletsik hi ama'n amanuom. 
\p  
\v 10 Takkha Pumi Nikhuo kha inruup kajuo angnga ajuosik eii. Khawa Nikhuoni khan marwaan ngaihi rasa inringtakle inruoiya lamangsik eii, lairalak-ah kaom rakip um kaangta lamangsik eii, halli nuoipilchung khat-um khanna kaom phur rakip alamangsik eii. \rq Matt 24:43; Luk 12:39; 1 Thes 5:2; Chonglar 16:15\rq* 
\p  
\v 11 Hiwa phur rakip hi hinthoa alamangsik ejarra nangni angkachang mi ngaikha ning-esikme? Nangni ringkhuo kha inthiang khat-um Pathian diang inpesuok ning-esik eii,  
\v 12 nangni'n Pathian Nikhuo kha ningngaak halli khawa Nikhuo kha innot-ah juonasik nangni ningmatorseng kha thoru, hiwa Nikhuo ajuotung phakhan marwaan ngaikha akaangwiak-ah inmangsik eii, halli lairalak-ah kaom rakip ngaikha akasa khan aminjungsik eii. 
\p  
\v 13 Takkha akathar marwaan ngai halli akathar nuoipilchung, mi kadik ngai omnasik inn ibooljei Pathian chong-inkhitna kha eini'n ningaak eii. \rq Isa 65:17; 66:22; Chonglar 21:1\rq* 
\p  
\v 14 Khawajarra, kiminriang kasap ngai, khawa Nikhuo kha ningngaak lai, Pathian mitmuwa kamasialmak khat-um inthiang ningchang nasik halli amale inruoiya kahoi-kadaiya omtheinasik nangni'n ningmatorseng kha thoru.  
\v 15 Minriang kaom nisuopui Paul ama'n Pathian ipe singna kha neimanna nangni diangnga imajia angnga, nangni sanring theinasik aphakacha kanapeii Nipumi deiraatna kha enru  
\v 16 Ama chemajia rakip ah hiwa chong jarhi ama'n amajia. Ama chemajia suungnga intak lekkhat kha om, khawa ngaikha akajet tungmak khat-um malung kangirmak mi ngai'n aleiilak Pathian-chong mun ngaikha katuunmak tiang inril angnga akatuunmak tiang inrilsik eii. Khawajarra intheinuo-ah mangnasik inhei-inchoi. 
\p  
\v 17 Takkha kiminriang kasap ngai, nangnichu, hiwahi ningjet suojei, dan kaneimak mi ngai masialna khan innaruoimak nasik halli nangirna mun kacheet-ah inphut napurmak nasik inringchakru.  
\v 18 Takkha Nipumi le Nakasanpa Jisu Christa jetna-theina riangwai tiang inchatleiya insoon chakru. Tuun khat-um kumsoot sik-ah ama lurna erase! Amen.